content_request: Donne moi le CA wave de janvier

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT
    daily_recharges.year AS year,
    daily_recharges.month AS month,
    SUM(daily_recharges.ca_wave) AS ca_wave
FROM
    daily_recharges
WHERE
    daily_recharges.month = 1
    AND daily_recharges.year = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE())
GROUP BY
    daily_recharges.year,
    daily_recharges.month;
